Configuration symlinks for ESP embedded linux - 3/18/16 brent@mbari.org
Typically Input to the mksymlinks as follows:

  mksymlinks rootfs < {this file}

To build forest of symlinks and empty directories under rootfs

Note:  remember to

   cd  /card
   rm  -rf card tmp var
   ln  -s  . card
   cd  /var
   mkdir -p log run lock

on any root filesystem copied to an (sd) card !!

============================================================

First the mountpoints and empty directories:

bufflehead/etc ->
bufflehead/home ->
raven/etc ->
raven/home ->

card/var/log ->
card/var/run ->
card/var/lock ->
flash ->

engineering ->
ESP ->
project ->
tempbox ->
u ->
ftp ->

boot ->
debug ->

============================================================

Next the symlinks:

etc/localtime -> /usr/share/zoneinfo/PST8PDT
etc/mtab -> /proc/mounts
etc/init.d -> rc.d/init.d

